 we rescale the Ehrenfest EM field in the form of
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\mathbf{E}_{Eh+R}=\mathbf{E}_{Eh}+\alpha\delta\mathbf{E}_{R},
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\mathbf{B}_{Eh+R}=\mathbf{B}_{Eh}+\beta\delta\mathbf{B}_{R},
