\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{1\leftarrow0}=\gamma_{\mathrm{vib}}e^{-\beta\varepsilon_{2}}$
\end_inset

 in terms of an empirical parameter 
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{\mathrm{vib}}$
\end_inset

.
 The parameter 
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{\mathrm{vib}}$
\end_inset

